WEBVTT

00:01:25.800 --> 00:01:30.800
"Sammy's Children's Day"

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:34.000
(Episode 1)

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:44.840
Watch out!

00:01:45.319 --> 00:01:46.319
Morning, Uncle Long.

00:01:46.359 --> 00:01:47.799
Rent's due! Hurry up!

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:48.519
Having a drink?

00:01:49.040 --> 00:01:50.040
Collecting rent!

00:01:50.319 --> 00:01:50.959
Ah San, you're back!

00:01:51.079 --> 00:01:52.079
Yeah, I'm back.

00:01:53.359 --> 00:01:55.039
You haven't paid yet!

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:56.400
Pay up!

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.280
Don't you run!

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:04.159
Stop right there!

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:08.960
You bastard! I'll hack you to death!

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:11.400
My name is He Chusan.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.640
I grew up in the Ganglong Walled City.

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:15.598
The Walled City is a lawless,

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:16.800
dark corner of the city.

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:20.319
It's full of the poor,
gamblers, and prostitutes.

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:23.759
Gangs of all sizes fight for control here,

00:02:24.039 --> 00:02:26.360
a never-ending cycle of blood and violence.

00:02:30.159 --> 00:02:31.478
But there are also many ordinary people

00:02:31.479 --> 00:02:33.479
living in the cracks of this chaos.

00:02:34.520 --> 00:02:35.400
Some of us

00:02:35.401 --> 00:02:36.761
do everything to avoid the triads,

00:02:37.199 --> 00:02:40.080
while others can't wait to join them.

00:02:43.639 --> 00:02:44.879
Fei Jie sent this over for you.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.000
Thanks.

00:02:48.159 --> 00:02:49.680
Uncle Abe, eat up. It's on the house.

00:02:49.719 --> 00:02:50.800
Well, don't mind if I do.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.240
Uncle Abe,

00:02:53.319 --> 00:02:54.735
do you know those guys with the knives?

00:02:54.759 --> 00:02:55.879
They looked so cool!

00:02:56.199 --> 00:02:57.199
Of course I know them.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:59.479
Those are Xia Liuyi's men.

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:03.479
He's the top enforcer in the Walled City.

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:05.639
The "Red Pole" hand-raised

00:03:05.719 --> 00:03:07.960
by the boss of Xiaoqi
Hall, Brother Chengqing.

00:03:08.199 --> 00:03:09.199
Red Pole?

00:03:09.759 --> 00:03:12.319
A Red Pole is the toughest fighter

00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:13.479
in the entire gang.

00:03:14.199 --> 00:03:15.199
Six years ago,

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:17.159
to rescue Brother Chengqing

00:03:17.199 --> 00:03:19.520
who was surrounded by enemies,

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:21.120
Xia Liuyi went in alone.

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:22.599
With a blade in each hand,

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:23.720
he just kept hacking away.

00:03:23.879 --> 00:03:25.000
He took down over forty men!

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:26.919
He chased them

00:03:27.120 --> 00:03:28.719
for three whole blocks.

00:03:30.319 --> 00:03:31.319
That fight

00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:34.879
is known as the "Dark Children's Day."

00:03:39.719 --> 00:03:40.719
Ever since then,

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:42.159
if anyone crosses him,

00:03:42.199 --> 00:03:44.039
he pulls out his twin blades

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:47.039
and "invites" them to
celebrate Children's Day.

00:03:47.240 --> 00:03:47.960
That's not right.

00:03:47.961 --> 00:03:49.159
Facing forty enemies,

00:03:49.400 --> 00:03:50.400
assuming each enemy has

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:51.240
a 20% chance

00:03:51.241 --> 00:03:52.719
of landing a hit on Xia Liuyi,

00:03:52.759 --> 00:03:54.158
the probability of him
taking down all forty

00:03:54.159 --> 00:03:55.598
without getting a single scratch

00:03:55.599 --> 00:03:57.919
is 0.8 to the power of 40.

00:03:58.159 --> 00:03:59.159
Which is roughly...

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:01.800
Uncle Abe,

00:04:02.159 --> 00:04:03.239
even if Xia Liuyi

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:05.279
is as skilled as you say,

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.199
the odds of him beating forty people

00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:07.560
without being injured

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:08.599
are practically zero.

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:11.080
Are you calling me a liar?

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:14.479
I was in Xiaoqi Hall back then.

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:15.600
I saw it with my own eyes!

00:04:16.399 --> 00:04:18.279
Combat still has to
follow the laws of science.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:21.040
Besides, gangs always
exaggerate their feats

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.119
to look more intimidating.

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:23.000
In reality,

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:24.959
gang life isn't just about breaking the law

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.000
and getting arrested.

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:27.959
Even in a small-scale brawl,

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:29.879
the mortality rate is as high as 80%.

00:04:31.319 --> 00:04:32.959
For guys like you two,

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:35.879
it's probably closer to 90%.

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:37.319
He Chusan!

00:04:37.480 --> 00:04:39.016
Don't think just because
you're in university

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.160
you can be so arrogant!

00:04:41.279 --> 00:04:42.399
Don't listen to him, boys.

00:04:42.879 --> 00:04:43.920
He's studied so much

00:04:44.079 --> 00:04:45.519
his brain has gone soft.

00:04:45.839 --> 00:04:46.319
Uncle Abe,

00:04:46.839 --> 00:04:47.839
you know,

00:04:48.399 --> 00:04:49.600
I read recently

00:04:49.839 --> 00:04:50.560
about people who

00:04:50.561 --> 00:04:52.040
recruit new members for gangs

00:04:52.519 --> 00:04:53.599
just to get a referral fee.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:57.040
You're not doing that, are you?

00:04:57.600 --> 00:04:59.080
He Chusan, you looking for a beating?

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.199
You old bastard!

00:05:01.360 --> 00:05:02.360
Get the hell out of here!

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:04.000
Last time you came here,

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:05.120
you ate and drank your fill

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:06.480
without paying a single cent!

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:08.239
And now you're bullying our Chusan?

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:09.680
I'll beat the life out of you!

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:10.199
Get him!

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:10.639
Fei Jie! Fei Jie!

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:11.199
Scram!

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:12.360
Get lost!

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:14.720
And you two!

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:16.519
Stop wasting your lives.

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:17.935
Look at your hair! What a mess!

00:05:17.959 --> 00:05:18.519
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

00:05:18.520 --> 00:05:20.000
Your heads look like feather dusters!

00:05:21.399 --> 00:05:22.560
What are you looking at?

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:24.199
Do you have any idea who he is?

00:05:24.839 --> 00:05:27.879
He's the first university
student from the Walled City!

00:05:28.079 --> 00:05:30.480
He got the top score in
the city to get into HKU!

00:05:31.160 --> 00:05:33.040
If he's willing to teach you something,

00:05:33.360 --> 00:05:35.480
you should be thanking your lucky stars!

00:05:35.959 --> 00:05:36.839
If you want to learn,

00:05:36.840 --> 00:05:39.519
learn from our Chusan.

00:05:41.399 --> 00:05:42.560
Take your time reading, dear.

00:05:48.040 --> 00:05:49.040
Lai Quan!

00:05:49.399 --> 00:05:50.399
Don't let me catch you.

00:05:50.759 --> 00:05:52.560
When I do, it won't just be about the 20k!

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:57.639
That bastard...

00:05:57.839 --> 00:05:58.839
Where is he?

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:00.440
Probably high on something.

00:06:00.600 --> 00:06:01.600
Ahao, we can't find him!

00:06:02.199 --> 00:06:03.559
Can't find him? Then keep looking!

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:04.680
Go! Move it!

00:06:11.240 --> 00:06:12.960
Fei Jie, I'm going to deliver the food now.

00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:16.920
Fei Jie, I'm heading out.

00:06:17.399 --> 00:06:18.560
Sammy, wait! Hold on.

00:06:18.680 --> 00:06:19.680
Here.

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:21.160
Take these two orders of beef offal.

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.759
Share them with your father.

00:06:22.800 --> 00:06:24.040
It's good for your health!

00:06:24.399 --> 00:06:25.000
Thanks, Fei Jie.

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.120
Don't mention it.

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:26.600
Come here.

00:06:26.759 --> 00:06:27.959
Let me help you with your bag.

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:30.399
Be careful on your way home.

00:06:30.519 --> 00:06:30.759
I will.

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:32.600
The gangs have been causing trouble lately.

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:33.680
Stay safe.

00:06:33.920 --> 00:06:34.680
I know.

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:35.720
Okay, see you!

00:06:40.360 --> 00:06:40.959
Sammy!

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:42.696
Help me take out the
trash, will you? Thanks.

00:06:42.720 --> 00:06:44.079
No problem, Uncle Shun. See ya!

00:06:55.879 --> 00:06:57.279
Are you blind?!

00:06:58.560 --> 00:06:59.560
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:00.879
Hand over the money!

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:01.759
Give it to me!

00:07:01.759 --> 00:07:02.399
This isn't my money!

00:07:02.519 --> 00:07:03.519
Don't run!

00:07:05.079 --> 00:07:05.680
Run!

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.519
You little brat, trying to run?

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:09.639
You think you can outrun me?

00:07:11.480 --> 00:07:12.480
Give it here!

00:07:12.759 --> 00:07:13.360
This money isn't mine!

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:14.680
Give it to me!

00:07:15.560 --> 00:07:17.120
I'll kill you, I swear!

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:18.720
Give it to me!

00:07:54.199 --> 00:07:56.560
L-Liuyi...

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:03.400
I invited you to celebrate,
but you didn't show.

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:07.400
Instead, you're out here
treating people to drinks?

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.000
Liuyi...

00:08:10.519 --> 00:08:12.160
It's just 20,000 dollars.

00:08:13.839 --> 00:08:14.399
Liuyi,

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:15.879
there's no need to be so angry.

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.639
I'll pay you back

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:21.560
another day, I promise!

00:08:22.199 --> 00:08:23.399
Die!

00:08:59.639 --> 00:09:01.000
Go ask around.

00:09:02.519 --> 00:09:04.960
When I invite someone, I
don't wait for "another day."

00:09:05.679 --> 00:09:08.039
Liuyi, I'm sorry!

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:10.840
I'm sorry, Liuyi!

00:09:29.360 --> 00:09:30.680
I chased you through nine blocks,

00:09:31.840 --> 00:09:32.840
Lai Quan.

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.200
And I finally caught you.

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:35.519
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

00:09:36.559 --> 00:09:37.878
He can't see me. He can't see me.

00:09:37.879 --> 00:09:38.879
He can't see me...

00:09:40.559 --> 00:09:41.559
Boss!

00:09:42.639 --> 00:09:43.839
Boss, what are you doing here?

00:09:44.759 --> 00:09:46.960
You didn't need to come
for something this small.

00:09:51.399 --> 00:09:52.639
I'm noting this failure down.

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:55.600
If you fail at the other task too,

00:09:56.759 --> 00:09:59.600
don't bother coming back to see me.

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:04.240
I'm sorry.

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:05.480
Let's go, Lai Quan.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:12.879
Liuyi is going to help you
celebrate Children's Day.

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:23.879
Boss!

00:10:25.559 --> 00:10:26.559
Boss, wait up!

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:27.720
Wait for us!

00:10:32.120 --> 00:10:33.120
What a terrible day.

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:34.759
I'm a dead man!

00:10:35.759 --> 00:10:37.480
The boss is going to kill me.

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:41.039
Mom, Dad...

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:42.840
I've failed you.

00:10:43.559 --> 00:10:45.919
Your son won't be
around to take care of you.

00:10:46.679 --> 00:10:48.360
If only I'd listened to you,

00:10:49.159 --> 00:10:51.079
I wouldn't have ended up like this.

00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:53.479
Do you need me to call a doctor?

00:10:53.480 --> 00:10:54.480
Dad!

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.120
HKU...

00:11:04.559 --> 00:11:05.559
Hong Kong...

00:11:08.600 --> 00:11:09.840
You're that university student!

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:21.080
Yes! Yes!

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:23.279
Talk about perfect timing!

00:11:24.559 --> 00:11:26.480
I'm the luckiest guy alive today!

00:11:33.759 --> 00:11:34.759
I'll kill you!

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:16.360
I'm so pissed off!

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:39.600
Ahao.

00:12:40.799 --> 00:12:41.799
Boss.

00:12:43.799 --> 00:12:44.799
Where's the dubbing?

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:48.200
This film doesn't have dubbing.

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:49.680
It's supposed to be like this.

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:53.000
Get out!

00:12:55.879 --> 00:12:56.879
Come back here.

00:12:58.399 --> 00:12:59.399
Boss.

00:13:00.279 --> 00:13:01.279
Who is he?

00:13:04.080 --> 00:13:05.080
A screenwriter.

00:13:06.399 --> 00:13:07.399
A real one.

00:13:12.960 --> 00:13:13.960
Boss.

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:17.960
Come closer.

00:13:20.039 --> 00:13:21.679
Do you think I'm three years old?

00:13:21.799 --> 00:13:22.480
B-Boss...

00:13:22.600 --> 00:13:23.320
Boss, I...

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:25.720
He's just a kid who sells beef offal.

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:27.480
No, Boss!

00:13:27.759 --> 00:13:28.080
He...

00:13:28.399 --> 00:13:29.559
He's that university student!

00:13:30.279 --> 00:13:31.919
The one in the papers with the fireworks!

00:13:33.679 --> 00:13:34.679
Look.

00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:39.080
See?

00:13:49.960 --> 00:13:50.960
Thank you, thank you.

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:55.600
You're disturbing my boss!

00:14:00.279 --> 00:14:01.320
Thank you, Commissioner.

00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:03.015
The Walled City finally
has a university student!

00:14:03.039 --> 00:14:04.840
The He family has produced a top scholar!

00:14:14.120 --> 00:14:14.519
Boss,

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:17.919
can I make up for my mistake now?

00:14:18.480 --> 00:14:19.480
Can I skip the beating?

00:14:23.759 --> 00:14:24.879
Lai Quan is right next door.

00:14:26.399 --> 00:14:27.399
You know what to do,

00:14:27.840 --> 00:14:28.759
don't you?

00:14:28.799 --> 00:14:29.799
Got it!

00:14:38.600 --> 00:14:39.600
Sit.

00:14:50.919 --> 00:14:52.039
Sit over there.

00:15:07.919 --> 00:15:09.119
What are they saying in there?

00:15:15.399 --> 00:15:17.759
I'm gonna make him
an offer he can't refuse.

00:15:23.320 --> 00:15:24.320
And this?

00:15:24.720 --> 00:15:26.639
Leave the rest to me.

00:15:32.240 --> 00:15:33.240
Not bad.

00:15:38.720 --> 00:15:39.720
Eat.

00:15:43.279 --> 00:15:44.639
No thanks.

00:15:44.879 --> 00:15:45.879
You little brat!

00:15:46.080 --> 00:15:47.255
When the boss tells you to eat, you eat!

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:49.135
How many times do I
have to tell you to shut up?

00:15:49.159 --> 00:15:50.159
Get out!

00:15:52.639 --> 00:15:53.639
It's fine.

00:15:54.039 --> 00:15:55.039
Go ahead and eat.

00:15:57.519 --> 00:15:59.119
Your family's beef offal is pretty good.

00:16:02.600 --> 00:16:04.159
Do you know why I brought you here

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:06.480
today?

00:16:09.120 --> 00:16:10.120
To buy beef offal?

00:16:11.279 --> 00:16:12.759
Did you study yourself stupid?

00:16:15.360 --> 00:16:17.519
Ever heard of a screenwriter?

00:16:20.519 --> 00:16:21.559
I want to make a movie.

00:16:23.360 --> 00:16:24.560
I want you to write the story.

00:16:25.720 --> 00:16:27.000
I'm a finance major.

00:16:27.159 --> 00:16:28.159
I don't know how.

00:16:28.759 --> 00:16:30.799
Lai Quan is a coward.

00:16:30.919 --> 00:16:32.199
He talked after just a few hits.

00:16:32.759 --> 00:16:34.480
He said his sister would pay the debt.

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:36.159
His sister is...

00:16:36.639 --> 00:16:38.719
the woman of Fat Seven,
the boss of the Hesheng triad.

00:16:39.559 --> 00:16:40.559
Lai Sanmei.

00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:43.320
Fat Seven really treats her well.

00:16:43.360 --> 00:16:44.720
Gave her a car, a house...

00:16:44.840 --> 00:16:46.799
diamond rings on every finger.

00:16:47.399 --> 00:16:49.519
That bastard has time to sleep with women,

00:16:49.879 --> 00:16:51.319
but when Brother Chengqing
invites him to dinner,

00:16:51.320 --> 00:16:52.320
what does Lai Sanmei say?

00:16:54.000 --> 00:16:56.200
Boss, do you know what she said?

00:16:58.206 --> 00:16:59.206
Talk!

00:17:00.159 --> 00:17:02.079
Just thinking about that
woman makes me furious.

00:17:02.320 --> 00:17:03.240
I called her,

00:17:03.241 --> 00:17:05.759
and she said she'd
cut ties with her brother.

00:17:06.160 --> 00:17:07.359
Then she just hung up on me!

00:17:07.679 --> 00:17:08.572
[Miscelaneous Cantonese swearing]

00:17:09.359 --> 00:17:10.359
Bring him in.

00:17:11.839 --> 00:17:12.839
Bring him here!

00:17:34.519 --> 00:17:35.119
Move it!

00:17:35.480 --> 00:17:35.960
Kneel!

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:37.000
Kneel down!

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:38.319
Liuyi...

00:17:38.400 --> 00:17:39.400
Liuyi!

00:17:39.599 --> 00:17:40.839
My sister won't acknowledge me.

00:17:40.960 --> 00:17:42.160
There's nothing I can do!

00:17:42.519 --> 00:17:44.159
Liuyi, I'm begging you, please let me go!

00:17:44.160 --> 00:17:45.160
Pull out his fingernails.

00:17:45.799 --> 00:17:46.880
No! Liuyi!

00:17:46.960 --> 00:17:47.960
Please let me go!

00:17:49.160 --> 00:17:49.640
Let's go!

00:17:49.759 --> 00:17:50.759
Move!

00:17:56.599 --> 00:17:57.599
Hold him down!

00:17:57.720 --> 00:17:58.720
Don't move!

00:18:05.680 --> 00:18:06.680
Another one.

00:18:30.359 --> 00:18:31.640
Think about it.

00:18:32.359 --> 00:18:33.599
One finger?

00:18:34.279 --> 00:18:35.799
Liuyi will help you decide.

00:18:36.720 --> 00:18:38.160
Three fingers.

00:18:41.559 --> 00:18:43.359
Liuyi, I'll find my mom!

00:18:43.599 --> 00:18:44.720
I'll find my mom!

00:18:45.039 --> 00:18:45.519
Liuyi!

00:18:45.759 --> 00:18:46.519
Please spare me!

00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:47.720
Please spare me!

00:18:48.400 --> 00:18:49.400
One.

00:18:50.000 --> 00:18:51.000
Liuyi, no!

00:18:51.359 --> 00:18:51.759
No!

00:18:51.920 --> 00:18:52.920
No!

00:18:53.240 --> 00:18:54.240
No, Liuyi!

00:19:00.599 --> 00:19:01.599
Wrap the finger up.

00:19:02.319 --> 00:19:03.519
Send it to Lai Sanmei.

00:19:04.079 --> 00:19:05.559
Tell her to give Fat Seven a message.

00:19:06.079 --> 00:19:07.119
Tonight at ten,

00:19:07.680 --> 00:19:08.720
Brother Chengqing

00:19:09.480 --> 00:19:11.039
will be at the Fengtai Nightclub

00:19:11.480 --> 00:19:12.480
waiting for him.

00:19:18.160 --> 00:19:18.480
Go!

00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:19.720
Move!

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:23.039
Boss, you...

00:19:23.480 --> 00:19:25.879
Catching Lai Quan was just a
way to get to Fat Seven, wasn't it?

00:19:26.200 --> 00:19:27.799
Stop wasting my time.

00:19:31.279 --> 00:19:32.759
Boss, you're truly a genius!

00:19:33.519 --> 00:19:34.519
You...

00:19:35.359 --> 00:19:36.359
I know this job.

00:19:36.599 --> 00:19:37.599
I love this job!

00:19:38.039 --> 00:19:40.480
I'm going crazy stuck at that film studio.

00:19:41.039 --> 00:19:42.000
I'm not sending you.

00:19:42.001 --> 00:19:43.559
I have something else for you to do.

00:19:47.359 --> 00:19:47.839
Who am I hitting?

00:19:48.319 --> 00:19:49.319
Just tell me where!

00:20:00.039 --> 00:20:01.480
You.

00:20:01.720 --> 00:20:02.720
What did you just say?

00:20:03.119 --> 00:20:04.119
I...

00:20:04.200 --> 00:20:06.799
I'm a finance major.

00:20:09.279 --> 00:20:10.279
And?

00:20:13.799 --> 00:20:14.920
I... I can write a script.

00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:18.720
Good.

00:20:20.599 --> 00:20:21.599
Go home.

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:27.680
Wait.

00:20:33.799 --> 00:20:34.799
Take the money.

00:20:36.119 --> 00:20:37.119
Work for Liuyi,

00:20:38.319 --> 00:20:39.639
and you'll never run out of cash.

00:20:41.279 --> 00:20:42.279
100,000 dollars.

00:20:45.839 --> 00:20:47.318
Dad works ten hours a day.

00:20:47.319 --> 00:20:48.495
He charges five dollars per patient.

00:20:48.519 --> 00:20:49.640
After the cost of medicine,

00:20:49.759 --> 00:20:51.095
his daily net income
is about forty dollars.

00:20:51.119 --> 00:20:52.199
That's about 14,000 a year.

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:54.360
Which means Dad would have to work

00:20:54.839 --> 00:20:55.856
every single day, rain or shine,

00:20:55.880 --> 00:20:57.720
for seven years to earn

00:21:00.480 --> 00:21:01.559
100,000 dollars.

00:21:03.559 --> 00:21:04.559
Oh my god.

00:21:09.400 --> 00:21:09.880
Sammy?

00:21:10.119 --> 00:21:11.119
You're back.

00:21:12.160 --> 00:21:12.480
Oh,

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:13.735
I left some food on the table.

00:21:13.759 --> 00:21:14.759
Why didn't you eat?

00:21:17.079 --> 00:21:18.079
Dad,

00:21:18.680 --> 00:21:20.200
I already ate at Fei Jie's.

00:21:21.839 --> 00:21:23.799
This boy... letting her
spend money on him again.

00:21:24.160 --> 00:21:25.559
How embarrassing.

00:21:26.279 --> 00:21:27.279
Dad.

00:21:31.039 --> 00:21:32.200
Dad, I'm tired.

00:21:32.279 --> 00:21:33.400
I'm going to bed.

00:21:35.119 --> 00:21:35.480
Okay.

00:21:36.119 --> 00:21:37.119
Get some sleep.

00:21:37.839 --> 00:21:39.119
You should rest too, Dad.

00:21:40.079 --> 00:21:41.079
I will.

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:42.680
Silly boy.

00:21:49.519 --> 00:21:50.519
No.

00:21:51.480 --> 00:21:52.960
I can't take money from the triads.

00:21:53.240 --> 00:21:54.520
It'll only bring trouble to Dad.

00:21:55.480 --> 00:21:56.880
Besides, Dad said

00:21:56.960 --> 00:21:58.759
Mom died because of them.

00:22:01.079 --> 00:22:02.160
If I take their money,

00:22:03.279 --> 00:22:05.119
I'm no better than they are.

00:22:24.400 --> 00:22:25.680
"101 Love Stories."

00:22:32.960 --> 00:22:34.000
They want a script,

00:22:35.559 --> 00:22:36.559
I'll give them a script.

00:22:38.480 --> 00:22:40.040
But I'm staying out of everything else.

00:23:04.160 --> 00:23:05.759
Time to clock out, girls!

00:23:06.519 --> 00:23:08.920
Liuyi has some important clients tonight.

00:23:09.200 --> 00:23:09.799
Aren't you happy?

00:23:09.799 --> 00:23:10.680
Let's go out and have some fun!

00:23:10.799 --> 00:23:11.799
Let's go, let's go!

00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:14.920
Boss, Fat Seven is here.

00:23:15.200 --> 00:23:16.200
Lai Sanmei is with him.

00:23:16.519 --> 00:23:17.959
When will Brother Chengqing be here?

00:23:25.559 --> 00:23:26.680
He's in Thailand.

00:23:27.759 --> 00:23:29.079
I'm hosting today.

00:23:47.519 --> 00:23:48.519
Seven.

00:23:48.759 --> 00:23:50.240
I've heard so much about you.

00:23:58.079 --> 00:23:59.399
Chengqing invited me,

00:23:59.400 --> 00:24:00.640
but he's late.

00:24:00.720 --> 00:24:01.880
What's that supposed to mean?

00:24:08.480 --> 00:24:09.480
Seven,

00:24:09.839 --> 00:24:11.199
Brother Chengqing prepared

00:24:11.200 --> 00:24:12.400
a special performance for you.

00:24:15.599 --> 00:24:16.240
But

00:24:16.480 --> 00:24:18.839
Uncle Yuan suddenly had a heart attack.

00:24:20.079 --> 00:24:21.400
Everyone knows

00:24:21.839 --> 00:24:23.119
Brother Chengqing

00:24:23.160 --> 00:24:24.839
is very close to Uncle Yuan.

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:26.079
As soon as he heard,

00:24:26.119 --> 00:24:27.279
he rushed to the hospital.

00:24:27.480 --> 00:24:28.480
But he

00:24:28.640 --> 00:24:31.480
didn't want you to miss
this incredible show,

00:24:32.160 --> 00:24:33.720
so he asked me to host you.

00:24:35.759 --> 00:24:38.559
If Chengqing isn't here,
who the hell are you?

00:24:40.559 --> 00:24:42.240
Come on, greet him!

00:24:55.880 --> 00:24:56.880
Greet him!

00:24:57.400 --> 00:24:59.200
Hello, Boss!

00:25:09.160 --> 00:25:10.000
Since you're already here,

00:25:10.079 --> 00:25:11.319
why not stay and have some fun?

00:25:11.480 --> 00:25:12.480
Fine, fine.

00:25:13.839 --> 00:25:14.839
Go.

00:25:37.000 --> 00:25:38.000
Seven,

00:25:38.799 --> 00:25:40.359
our nightclub isn't bad, right?

00:25:41.480 --> 00:25:42.640
Look,

00:25:42.799 --> 00:25:44.798
about opening a drug den on your turf...

00:25:44.799 --> 00:25:45.799
Seven.

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:51.480
Liuyi, you're here.

00:25:51.640 --> 00:25:52.880
I saw the "Closed" sign outside

00:25:53.079 --> 00:25:54.000
and thought some punks

00:25:54.001 --> 00:25:55.761
were slacking off and
partying on their own.

00:25:58.279 --> 00:25:59.279
Brother Xu.

00:25:59.559 --> 00:26:00.559
Brother Xu.

00:26:04.400 --> 00:26:05.599
Fat Seven, you're here too!

00:26:09.119 --> 00:26:09.799
Liuyi,

00:26:10.079 --> 00:26:11.680
this is where you're wrong.

00:26:12.640 --> 00:26:14.599
The boss is in Thailand,

00:26:14.960 --> 00:26:16.599
and Seven is here to play.

00:26:16.799 --> 00:26:18.880
I should be the one hosting him.

00:26:19.400 --> 00:26:20.480
Right, Seven?

00:26:21.039 --> 00:26:22.039
What's going on?

00:26:24.039 --> 00:26:25.160
Chengqing isn't here,

00:26:28.559 --> 00:26:29.559
Xia Liuyi,

00:26:30.839 --> 00:26:31.880
are you playing me?

00:26:33.000 --> 00:26:35.176
If Chengqing isn't here, do you really
think you're important enough to invite me?

00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:36.758
Alright, Seven, calm down.

00:26:36.759 --> 00:26:37.799
This is our turf.

00:26:38.240 --> 00:26:39.880
Boss, do we move?

00:26:41.640 --> 00:26:42.680
Brother Chengqing is here!

00:26:42.839 --> 00:26:43.160
Boss.

00:26:43.480 --> 00:26:43.759
Boss.

00:26:43.799 --> 00:26:44.359
Move, move!

00:26:44.400 --> 00:26:45.400
Boss.

00:26:45.640 --> 00:26:46.640
Boss.

00:26:47.119 --> 00:26:48.119
Boss.

00:27:02.319 --> 00:27:02.720
Boss.

00:27:03.160 --> 00:27:04.799
Seven, long time no see.

00:27:05.559 --> 00:27:07.239
Something urgent came up as I was leaving,

00:27:07.480 --> 00:27:09.120
so I sent my brother to keep you company.

00:27:09.680 --> 00:27:10.680
You don't think

00:27:11.119 --> 00:27:13.160
I was trying to snub you, do you?

00:27:15.960 --> 00:27:16.960
No.

00:27:17.400 --> 00:27:19.200
Everyone has things
they can't get away from.

00:27:19.559 --> 00:27:20.920
We're brothers, aren't we?

00:27:21.720 --> 00:27:23.200
I knew I could count on you.

00:27:23.906 --> 00:27:25.266
You've always been generous.

00:27:35.799 --> 00:27:36.799
Unlike me,

00:27:38.039 --> 00:27:39.359
I've always been the skinny type.

00:27:47.920 --> 00:27:49.279
Since you're so busy,

00:27:49.680 --> 00:27:50.839
I'll keep it short.

00:27:51.960 --> 00:27:52.960
I wanted to talk to you

00:27:54.000 --> 00:27:55.759
about the nightclub business.

00:28:00.480 --> 00:28:02.200
Whatever you say goes.

00:28:03.799 --> 00:28:04.999
I heard you recently

00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:06.799
got the best shipment from Thailand.

00:28:07.640 --> 00:28:09.240
If I can make money while doing nothing,

00:28:09.480 --> 00:28:10.720
of course I'm in.

00:28:12.079 --> 00:28:13.079
However,

00:28:13.599 --> 00:28:14.720
I have a brother-in-law

00:28:14.920 --> 00:28:15.920
named Lai Quan.

00:28:16.759 --> 00:28:17.839
Liuyi told me about it.

00:28:18.759 --> 00:28:20.039
His men grabbed the wrong person

00:28:20.160 --> 00:28:21.759
and he's been worried sick.

00:28:22.319 --> 00:28:23.319
So,

00:28:23.480 --> 00:28:25.000
I told him to come here

00:28:25.400 --> 00:28:26.640
and apologize to you in person.

00:28:29.240 --> 00:28:30.240
Seven,

00:28:30.799 --> 00:28:31.960
my men grabbed the wrong guy.

00:28:32.680 --> 00:28:33.680
It was my mistake.

00:28:35.559 --> 00:28:36.559
I'll drink to that.

00:28:47.279 --> 00:28:48.559
It's fine.

00:28:48.960 --> 00:28:49.960
Don't worry about it.

00:28:51.359 --> 00:28:52.480
He has to.

00:28:53.720 --> 00:28:55.400
He'll be managing

00:28:55.720 --> 00:28:57.080
the Hesheng nightclub from now on.

00:29:01.759 --> 00:29:04.119
But he goes and messes with
the wrong person right away.

00:29:05.839 --> 00:29:06.839
What's that about?

00:29:11.599 --> 00:29:12.480
We're having a good time today,

00:29:12.481 --> 00:29:14.160
let's not talk about this crap, okay?

00:29:15.160 --> 00:29:15.680
Liuyi,

00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:17.000
pour Seven a drink.

00:29:17.079 --> 00:29:18.079
Okay.

00:29:18.200 --> 00:29:19.200
Pouring.

00:29:19.680 --> 00:29:20.680
Seven,

00:29:20.866 --> 00:29:22.146
please forgive my mistake.

00:29:22.880 --> 00:29:23.920
This drink is for you.

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:25.759
Bottoms up.

00:29:29.039 --> 00:29:30.039
Seven,

00:29:30.079 --> 00:29:31.799
it really was just a misunderstanding.

00:29:31.839 --> 00:29:33.200
Work hard, kid.

00:29:33.480 --> 00:29:35.319
You've got a good boss looking out for you.

00:29:35.680 --> 00:29:38.039
Ahao, see Seven out.

00:29:38.920 --> 00:29:39.359
Akun,

00:29:39.559 --> 00:29:40.775
take our brothers to check out the place.

00:29:40.799 --> 00:29:41.799
Let's go.

00:29:42.359 --> 00:29:43.359
Okay.

00:29:43.680 --> 00:29:44.680
This way.

00:29:44.839 --> 00:29:45.839
This way.

00:29:45.864 --> 00:29:47.490
[More Cantonese swearing]

00:29:53.839 --> 00:29:55.119
Are you kidding me?

00:29:55.200 --> 00:29:56.200
That damn Fat Seven...

00:29:56.279 --> 00:29:57.598
he can really drink.

00:29:57.599 --> 00:29:58.920
He drank all my booze!

00:29:59.880 --> 00:30:01.039
Unbelievable.

00:30:22.720 --> 00:30:23.720
Brother,

00:30:26.119 --> 00:30:27.480
why did you come back so suddenly?

00:30:29.000 --> 00:30:30.000
Brother,

00:30:30.880 --> 00:30:33.079
are you really giving me this nightclub?

00:30:35.000 --> 00:30:36.400
Are you doubting me?

00:30:37.640 --> 00:30:38.800
When have I ever lied to you?

00:30:43.160 --> 00:30:44.799
If I hadn't come back early,

00:30:46.759 --> 00:30:48.199
how were you going to fix this mess?

00:30:49.039 --> 00:30:50.079
Brother,

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:52.720
I'm just lucky.

00:30:52.920 --> 00:30:54.839
I have you to clean up after me, right?

00:30:56.079 --> 00:30:58.880
Besides, the movie studio

00:30:58.920 --> 00:31:00.119
and the money laundering...

00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:03.640
Cui Dongdong should be handling that.

00:31:04.799 --> 00:31:06.480
Brother, what am I?

00:31:07.599 --> 00:31:08.920
A Red Pole!

00:31:10.000 --> 00:31:12.200
I should be on the front lines for you,

00:31:13.599 --> 00:31:14.960
taking over territory.

00:31:16.160 --> 00:31:18.960
Being stuck at the
studio every day is boring.

00:31:20.480 --> 00:31:21.480
Listen to me.

00:31:22.240 --> 00:31:23.920
The nightclub is yours,

00:31:24.759 --> 00:31:26.680
but the studio is still your priority.

00:31:27.880 --> 00:31:28.880
One month.

00:31:29.400 --> 00:31:30.599
I'm giving you one month

00:31:30.960 --> 00:31:32.200
to get that movie made.

00:31:32.599 --> 00:31:33.599
Go oversee it yourself.

00:31:34.279 --> 00:31:35.599
And spend some time with Xiaoman.

00:31:35.880 --> 00:31:37.319
No, Brother!

00:31:37.599 --> 00:31:40.039
The studio is so dull.

00:31:40.240 --> 00:31:41.960
Every time I'm there,

00:31:42.079 --> 00:31:43.079
I feel like...

00:31:43.359 --> 00:31:44.359
Brother?

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:47.160
Brother, are you okay?

00:31:53.200 --> 00:31:54.200
I'm fine.

00:31:54.519 --> 00:31:55.519
I've just been busy.

00:31:55.920 --> 00:31:56.920
A bit tired.

00:31:57.759 --> 00:31:58.919
You've been working too hard.

00:31:59.000 --> 00:32:00.000
Take it easy, Brother.

00:32:16.359 --> 00:32:17.639
I only want what's best for you.

00:32:23.200 --> 00:32:24.680
I've told you so many times,

00:32:25.279 --> 00:32:27.439
if you wear a suit, you
have to tie your tie properly.

00:32:28.079 --> 00:32:29.119
But you never listen.

00:32:30.039 --> 00:32:31.039
You rebel.

00:32:32.000 --> 00:32:33.000
I'm leaving.

00:32:35.960 --> 00:32:37.359
Get some rest, Brother.

00:32:37.960 --> 00:32:38.960
See ya.

00:32:47.200 --> 00:32:47.640
Boss,

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:50.279
does that mean we have
to go back to the studio?

00:32:50.680 --> 00:32:52.039
Are you stupid?

00:32:52.839 --> 00:32:54.200
The movie has to be made.

00:32:54.400 --> 00:32:55.920
That's a direct order from my brother.

00:32:56.680 --> 00:32:57.680
But

00:32:58.799 --> 00:33:00.200
that director you found

00:33:00.720 --> 00:33:02.640
says it'll take a month.

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:06.000
What's he trying to do?

00:33:06.119 --> 00:33:07.680
Win an Oscar?

00:33:12.920 --> 00:33:13.920
Reporting, Boss!

00:33:14.240 --> 00:33:15.240
We'll finish the movie

00:33:15.599 --> 00:33:17.160
in just ten days.

00:33:17.880 --> 00:33:19.880
And for the rest of the month,

00:33:21.119 --> 00:33:25.480
we'll keep partying at the nightclub!

00:33:25.680 --> 00:33:26.759
Do you want to die?

00:33:27.400 --> 00:33:27.759
Boss!

00:33:27.799 --> 00:33:28.799
I'll kick your ass!

00:33:29.759 --> 00:33:30.279
Don't run!

00:33:30.480 --> 00:33:31.480
Boss!

00:33:40.039 --> 00:33:41.079
Hao Chengqing,

00:33:41.519 --> 00:33:42.799
for the sake of some pretty boy,

00:33:43.160 --> 00:33:45.920
you'd throw me away, the brother
who's been through hell with you?

00:33:56.599 --> 00:33:59.559
The midnight bell has just struck,

00:33:59.960 --> 00:34:02.920
The neon lights are flashing bright.

00:34:03.279 --> 00:34:06.279
Who's looking for escape in a glass?

00:34:06.880 --> 00:34:09.519
Who's causing trouble on the dance floor?

00:34:11.159 --> 00:34:14.480
When the music starts,
don't think too much,

00:34:14.880 --> 00:34:18.198
Let your body move on its own.

00:34:18.199 --> 00:34:20.479
Drown out all your worries,

00:34:20.480 --> 00:34:22.919
Follow the rhythm and dance like crazy.

00:34:22.920 --> 00:34:23.519
That was great!

00:34:23.800 --> 00:34:24.800
You're the best, Boss!

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:26.440
I'm not going to a nightclub!

00:34:26.480 --> 00:34:27.480
I won't go!

00:34:27.920 --> 00:34:29.639
Let me go! Let me go!

00:34:30.639 --> 00:34:35.518
In this moment, who cares about tomorrow?

00:34:35.519 --> 00:34:36.519
Boss.

00:34:37.480 --> 00:34:38.480
Boss.

00:34:39.960 --> 00:34:41.159
I brought the kid.

00:34:41.480 --> 00:34:42.480
Anything else?

00:34:42.599 --> 00:34:43.599
Go have fun.

00:34:43.840 --> 00:34:44.840
Okay!

00:34:45.039 --> 00:34:46.119
He's here!

00:34:46.199 --> 00:34:47.199
Keep partying!

00:34:54.920 --> 00:34:55.960
University student.

00:34:56.480 --> 00:34:57.280
It's been three days.

00:34:57.400 --> 00:34:58.400
Where's the script?

00:35:22.960 --> 00:35:24.159
The Little Mermaid,

00:35:24.199 --> 00:35:26.599
to see her human prince again,

00:35:28.880 --> 00:35:30.920
makes a deal with the Sea Witch.

00:35:31.920 --> 00:35:34.480
She endures the pain of losing her tail

00:35:41.280 --> 00:35:42.280
and fins...

00:35:44.960 --> 00:35:45.960
Keep reading.

00:35:51.639 --> 00:35:53.559
In exchange for legs to walk on land.

00:35:53.960 --> 00:35:55.158
When she steps onto the shore,

00:35:55.159 --> 00:35:56.336
every step feels like walking on knives.

00:35:56.360 --> 00:35:57.360
Louder!

00:35:59.159 --> 00:36:02.000
Still, she searches hopefully
for her prince.

00:36:02.239 --> 00:36:03.400
But she doesn't know

00:36:03.599 --> 00:36:05.519
that in the shadows of this port city,

00:36:06.320 --> 00:36:09.519
there lurks a terrifying

00:36:09.760 --> 00:36:11.000
twin-blade-wielding triad boss.

00:36:11.159 --> 00:36:12.479
The boss controls

00:36:12.480 --> 00:36:13.760
the city's underground trade.

00:36:16.920 --> 00:36:19.000
And he uses twin blades.

00:36:21.760 --> 00:36:23.000
Sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?

00:36:42.199 --> 00:36:43.400
What are you ducking for?

00:36:44.960 --> 00:36:46.200
Don't try to be clever with me.

00:36:47.079 --> 00:36:48.519
Mocking your boss in your writing?

00:36:49.519 --> 00:36:50.519
University student,

00:36:51.039 --> 00:36:52.840
that's not how you earn money.

00:36:53.719 --> 00:36:54.719
Rewrite it.

00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:55.920
Okay.

00:36:56.000 --> 00:36:57.000
Now.

00:37:10.199 --> 00:37:13.399
The midnight bell has just struck,

00:37:13.400 --> 00:37:15.359
The neon lights are flashing bright.

00:37:15.360 --> 00:37:16.679
I'm a finance major,

00:37:17.000 --> 00:37:17.840
I don't know how to write scripts.

00:37:17.841 --> 00:37:20.078
Who's looking for escape in a glass?

00:37:20.079 --> 00:37:23.760
Who's causing trouble on the dance floor?

00:37:24.639 --> 00:37:27.880
When the music starts,
don't think too much,

00:37:28.280 --> 00:37:31.638
Let your body move on its own.

00:37:31.639 --> 00:37:34.238
Drown out all your worries,

00:37:34.239 --> 00:37:36.879
Follow the rhythm and dance like crazy.

00:37:36.880 --> 00:37:38.999
Heart's pounding fast,

00:37:39.000 --> 00:37:41.359
Alcohol's burning bright.

00:37:41.360 --> 00:37:47.119
In this moment, who cares about tomorrow?

00:38:59.599 --> 00:39:00.599
Who is it?

00:39:03.320 --> 00:39:04.320
Boss!

00:39:07.280 --> 00:39:08.280
Boss!

00:39:09.320 --> 00:39:09.880
Brother Chengqing

00:39:10.039 --> 00:39:10.639
is coming to the studio

00:39:10.840 --> 00:39:11.320
to check on us!

00:39:11.679 --> 00:39:12.679
His wife is with him too.

00:39:12.760 --> 00:39:13.920
They're already on their way!

00:39:15.480 --> 00:39:16.480
Wake everyone up! Now!

00:39:17.800 --> 00:39:18.800
Get up!

00:39:19.239 --> 00:39:20.239
Get up!

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:21.239
Back to the studio!

00:39:21.639 --> 00:39:22.639
I have class!

00:39:22.960 --> 00:39:23.320
Let's go!

00:39:23.480 --> 00:39:24.000
Ten minutes.

00:39:24.119 --> 00:39:25.119
Forget about class!

00:39:25.159 --> 00:39:25.760
I'm giving you ten minutes

00:39:25.760 --> 00:39:26.760
to write a new story,

00:39:26.840 --> 00:39:27.840
or I'll kill you!

00:39:28.719 --> 00:39:29.719
Wait a second!

00:39:29.920 --> 00:39:30.599
Hurry up!

00:39:30.880 --> 00:39:32.560
Or I'll help you celebrate Children's Day!

00:39:34.800 --> 00:39:35.320
Assistant Director!

00:39:35.639 --> 00:39:36.639
Get moving!

00:39:37.480 --> 00:39:38.480
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

00:39:38.559 --> 00:39:39.559
All departments, move it!

00:39:39.840 --> 00:39:40.840
Get to work!

00:39:40.880 --> 00:39:41.880
Be quick about it!

00:39:42.760 --> 00:39:43.599
And over here, move it!

00:39:43.599 --> 00:39:44.599
Hurry up!

00:39:45.039 --> 00:39:46.039
Move!

00:39:46.079 --> 00:39:47.079
Everyone, get moving!

00:39:48.719 --> 00:39:49.719
Boss.

00:40:07.320 --> 00:40:07.760
Boss.

00:40:08.159 --> 00:40:08.639
Assistant Director!

00:40:08.960 --> 00:40:09.960
I'm here, I'm here!

00:40:10.280 --> 00:40:11.280
Come here.

00:40:17.719 --> 00:40:18.919
Ahao, help me with my clothes.

00:40:24.480 --> 00:40:24.960
Brother Chengqing, Sister-in-law.

00:40:25.480 --> 00:40:26.480
Boss.

00:40:27.599 --> 00:40:27.880
Boss.

00:40:28.280 --> 00:40:28.719
Boss.

00:40:28.880 --> 00:40:29.880
Boss.

00:40:30.360 --> 00:40:30.880
Come, come.

00:40:31.199 --> 00:40:31.719
This way.

00:40:32.119 --> 00:40:33.399
Take her to get her makeup done.

00:40:33.920 --> 00:40:34.320
This way.

00:40:34.599 --> 00:40:35.959
Let's go take some costume photos.

00:40:40.719 --> 00:40:41.320
Boss, this way.

00:40:41.679 --> 00:40:42.679
Please, sit.

00:40:46.360 --> 00:40:47.360
Where's Liuyi?

00:40:47.679 --> 00:40:48.679
Liuyi?

00:40:48.880 --> 00:40:50.319
He's out with the screenwriter
looking for inspiration

00:40:50.320 --> 00:40:50.880
for the script.

00:40:50.920 --> 00:40:51.719
I heard

00:40:51.720 --> 00:40:53.599
he's been hanging out
in Lan Kwai Fong lately.

00:40:54.280 --> 00:40:55.119
That's not true.

00:40:55.119 --> 00:40:56.000
It's all thanks to Liuyi.

00:40:56.001 --> 00:40:57.681
He took me everywhere to find inspiration.

00:40:58.320 --> 00:40:59.039
Otherwise,

00:40:59.079 --> 00:41:00.695
I never could have
written such a great story.

00:41:00.719 --> 00:41:01.800
Of course!

00:41:02.039 --> 00:41:04.159
If Brother Chengqing wants
our boss to make a movie,

00:41:04.400 --> 00:41:06.559
it has to be an Oscar-worthy one.

00:41:06.679 --> 00:41:07.119
Don't worry.

00:41:07.639 --> 00:41:08.519
If you need anything in the future,

00:41:08.639 --> 00:41:09.360
just let me know.

00:41:09.639 --> 00:41:10.879
Liuyi will definitely help you.

00:41:12.360 --> 00:41:12.840
Brother,

00:41:13.320 --> 00:41:14.320
what are you doing here?

00:41:15.960 --> 00:41:17.480
You're dressed just like Chow Yun-fat.

00:41:18.639 --> 00:41:20.360
I came to see how your Oscar-winning movie

00:41:20.719 --> 00:41:21.719
is coming along.

00:41:23.000 --> 00:41:24.039
It's going great.

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:30.160
Xiaoman wanted to come out for a walk too.

00:41:39.119 --> 00:41:40.119
Sister.

00:41:41.159 --> 00:41:42.159
Don't scare her.

00:41:42.880 --> 00:41:44.560
The doctor said she shouldn't be startled.

00:41:46.079 --> 00:41:47.079
What did the doctor say?

00:41:47.719 --> 00:41:48.719
Same as always.

00:41:49.559 --> 00:41:51.079
She's becoming more and more confused.

00:41:51.559 --> 00:41:52.639
The medicine isn't helping.

00:41:53.480 --> 00:41:54.960
She often mistakes people for others.

00:41:55.000 --> 00:41:56.600
Sometimes she doesn't even recognize me.

00:42:03.960 --> 00:42:04.960
This is our screenwriter.

00:42:07.039 --> 00:42:08.039
Let me introduce you.

00:42:08.079 --> 00:42:09.320
A top student from HKU,

00:42:09.599 --> 00:42:11.159
known as the "Drama-Obsessed Genius."

00:42:11.760 --> 00:42:13.079
He loves creating stories.

00:42:17.800 --> 00:42:19.239
Drama-Obsessed Genius?

00:42:19.960 --> 00:42:21.119
Tell us about your script.

00:42:28.880 --> 00:42:29.880
Read it!

00:42:37.519 --> 00:42:39.158
A dashing, carefree triad enforcer

00:42:39.159 --> 00:42:41.319
falls in love with a beautiful
woman from the streets.

00:42:41.719 --> 00:42:44.280
But after their romantic encounter,

00:42:46.159 --> 00:42:48.519
the woman is taken by a rival gang.

00:42:48.880 --> 00:42:51.119
The rival gang, who had long desired her,

00:42:51.480 --> 00:42:52.896
takes advantage of the enforcer's absence

00:42:52.920 --> 00:42:54.480
and kidnaps her in a swift strike,

00:42:54.920 --> 00:42:56.960
intending to use her for
blackmail and humiliation.

00:42:57.760 --> 00:42:59.639
One man with twin
blades takes on forty men...

00:42:59.760 --> 00:43:01.639
This sounds just like

00:43:01.880 --> 00:43:04.000
when our boss rescued Brother Chengqing.

00:43:04.679 --> 00:43:06.760
In the end, the enforcer
and the beautiful woman

00:43:06.800 --> 00:43:08.000
live happily ever after...

00:43:15.679 --> 00:43:16.400
You little...

00:43:16.400 --> 00:43:17.280
How dare you write this crap!

00:43:17.360 --> 00:43:17.920
You want to die?

00:43:17.960 --> 00:43:18.960
I think it's pretty good.

00:43:20.079 --> 00:43:21.079
Let's film it.

00:43:27.920 --> 00:43:29.400
Once Xiaoman is done with her photos,

00:43:29.760 --> 00:43:31.680
I'll take you both back
to the villa for dinner.

00:43:31.719 --> 00:43:32.719
But Brother,

00:43:33.039 --> 00:43:34.360
his script is basically...

00:43:36.000 --> 00:43:37.079
I've told you many times,

00:43:37.920 --> 00:43:40.080
if you wear a suit, you
have to tie your tie properly.

00:43:42.480 --> 00:43:44.840
If you don't know how, you'll
just end up making a mess.

00:43:46.039 --> 00:43:47.039
You rebel.

00:43:47.599 --> 00:43:48.599
I'm off.

00:43:51.519 --> 00:43:52.519
Take care, Brother.

00:44:08.119 --> 00:44:09.119
Ahao,

00:44:10.320 --> 00:44:11.456
take him down and check him over.

00:44:11.480 --> 00:44:12.079
Got it.

00:44:12.480 --> 00:44:13.480
If nothing's broken,

00:44:13.519 --> 00:44:14.519
keep writing that script.

00:44:14.800 --> 00:44:15.800
Get up.

00:44:15.960 --> 00:44:16.320
Let's go.

00:44:16.400 --> 00:44:17.400
Get up!

00:44:35.039 --> 00:44:36.760
Triads are all thugs.

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:38.719
And Xia Liuyi

00:44:38.800 --> 00:44:40.360
is the worst of them all.

00:44:48.559 --> 00:44:51.039
I've missed two days of class already.

00:44:53.119 --> 00:44:54.360
My scholarship is gone.

00:44:55.239 --> 00:45:00.960
Will I have to ask Dad
for next year's tuition?

00:45:01.960 --> 00:45:03.320
He works so hard.

00:45:04.480 --> 00:45:05.480
You wrote this?

00:45:07.880 --> 00:45:09.079
It's really good.

00:45:17.360 --> 00:45:18.360
What's wrong?

00:45:18.599 --> 00:45:19.599
Are you not feeling well?

00:45:19.679 --> 00:45:20.679
I'm fine.

00:45:23.880 --> 00:45:24.880
Who did this to you?

00:45:28.320 --> 00:45:30.079
It was Xia Liuyi.

00:45:31.400 --> 00:45:32.560
Liuyi is being naughty again.

00:45:32.880 --> 00:45:33.519
I'll go talk to him for you.

00:45:33.719 --> 00:45:34.719
No, no, no!

00:45:35.920 --> 00:45:36.920
It's okay.

00:45:37.920 --> 00:45:38.920
I have to.

00:45:40.480 --> 00:45:41.480
He's always like this.

00:45:41.679 --> 00:45:42.839
That's why he has no friends.

00:45:58.039 --> 00:45:59.320
But don't blame him.

00:46:00.480 --> 00:46:01.920
He just has no one to play with.

00:46:10.480 --> 00:46:11.480
Back then,

00:46:11.519 --> 00:46:12.519
he was so pitiful.

00:46:13.800 --> 00:46:14.840
It was just the two of us.

00:46:18.480 --> 00:46:20.000
Are you the lead actress?

00:46:22.199 --> 00:46:23.320
Why aren't you filming?

00:46:25.039 --> 00:46:26.039
Filming?

00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:33.280
What's the point?

00:46:35.000 --> 00:46:36.320
No matter how much I film,

00:46:37.519 --> 00:46:38.519
he'll never watch it.

00:46:40.840 --> 00:46:41.840
I thought

00:46:43.079 --> 00:46:44.079
I loved him,

00:46:46.719 --> 00:46:47.840
and he loved me too.

00:46:49.280 --> 00:46:50.920
That what we had was love.

00:46:54.360 --> 00:46:55.360
But...

00:47:02.199 --> 00:47:03.679
I heard you're a genius screenwriter.

00:47:04.280 --> 00:47:05.520
You must know a lot about love.

00:47:12.393 --> 00:47:13.712
Genius screenwriter?

00:47:14.199 --> 00:47:15.480
He just made that up.

00:47:20.920 --> 00:47:22.480
Then can you tell me,

00:47:23.079 --> 00:47:24.119
what is love?

00:47:27.599 --> 00:47:28.599
Love?

00:47:30.280 --> 00:47:31.280
Xiaoman!

00:47:32.480 --> 00:47:33.480
Xiaoman!

00:47:34.239 --> 00:47:34.880
Time for photos.

00:47:35.000 --> 00:47:36.080
We're just waiting for you.

00:47:37.199 --> 00:47:38.199
Xiaoman.

00:47:39.239 --> 00:47:40.199
Call her Sister-in-law!

00:47:40.199 --> 00:47:41.199
Liuyi,

00:47:42.280 --> 00:47:43.639
you can't just hit people.

00:47:43.719 --> 00:47:44.719
It's not nice.

00:47:46.280 --> 00:47:47.280
Okay, okay.

00:47:47.480 --> 00:47:48.119
I'm sorry.

00:47:48.400 --> 00:47:49.400
I won't do it again.

00:47:50.159 --> 00:47:51.480
Liuyi is a good boy.

00:47:53.920 --> 00:47:54.360
Alright.

00:47:54.679 --> 00:47:55.679
Let's go take the photos.

00:47:55.760 --> 00:47:56.679
Everyone's waiting.

00:47:56.719 --> 00:47:57.280
Just for you.

00:47:57.280 --> 00:47:58.280
Let's go, let's go.

00:48:00.960 --> 00:48:04.520
Next time, tell me the answer.

00:48:09.480 --> 00:48:10.920
I'll be watching you.

00:48:11.360 --> 00:48:12.599
Okay, okay.

00:48:13.199 --> 00:48:14.480
Let's go. Photos!

00:48:15.079 --> 00:48:16.079
Let's go.

00:48:27.178 --> 00:48:28.935
[Liuyi Children's...]

00:48:28.960 --> 00:48:30.320
I should go find some inspiration.

00:48:53.519 --> 00:48:54.599
Like a dog,

00:48:54.679 --> 00:48:55.679
barking and barking.

00:49:05.480 --> 00:49:06.480
What is love?

00:49:09.360 --> 00:49:10.719
Love is when someone

00:49:11.320 --> 00:49:12.840
is willing to risk everything for you.

00:49:13.480 --> 00:49:15.280
They'd even give up their life

00:49:16.239 --> 00:49:17.519
just to save you.

00:49:18.679 --> 00:49:19.936
They aren't afraid of getting hurt,

00:49:19.960 --> 00:49:20.960
or the pain.

00:49:21.400 --> 00:49:22.960
They'd even die for you.

00:49:24.039 --> 00:49:25.639
They'll stand up for you

00:49:26.199 --> 00:49:27.239
when you're most helpless.

00:49:28.159 --> 00:49:29.759
And when you're on the brink of despair,

00:49:30.119 --> 00:49:31.119
they'll hold you tight.

00:49:35.280 --> 00:49:36.280
Time to eat!

00:49:37.320 --> 00:49:38.360
Dinner's ready!

00:49:38.960 --> 00:49:39.360
Let's eat!

00:49:39.840 --> 00:49:40.840
Food's here!

00:49:41.960 --> 00:49:42.960
Time to eat, Boss!

00:49:44.760 --> 00:49:45.760
Eat first, play later!

00:49:46.599 --> 00:49:47.239
Come and eat!

00:49:47.280 --> 00:49:47.760
Dinner time!

00:49:47.840 --> 00:49:48.920
Food's ready! Food's ready!

00:49:50.000 --> 00:49:51.000
Let's eat!

00:50:01.840 --> 00:50:02.840
He Chusan!

00:50:03.000 --> 00:50:03.639
Get over here and eat!

00:50:03.679 --> 00:50:04.679
Coming!

00:50:15.400 --> 00:50:20.920
Boss, Boss, Boss!

00:50:22.159 --> 00:50:23.159
What happened?

00:50:33.480 --> 00:50:34.480
If one day,

00:50:35.400 --> 00:50:36.559
someone like that

00:50:36.920 --> 00:50:38.119
appears in your life,

00:50:39.159 --> 00:50:40.280
don't hesitate.

00:50:41.159 --> 00:50:42.159
Don't run away.

00:50:43.280 --> 00:50:44.480
You must use all your strength

00:50:44.960 --> 00:50:45.960
to hold onto them.

00:50:49.719 --> 00:50:50.719
Are you okay?

00:50:51.400 --> 00:50:52.400
I'm fine.

00:50:55.880 --> 00:50:57.238
Boss, how are you?

00:50:57.239 --> 00:50:58.239
Are you alright?

00:51:01.480 --> 00:51:02.480
How are you feeling?

00:51:02.840 --> 00:51:03.760
Are you hurt?

00:51:03.761 --> 00:51:04.800
Because their eyes

00:51:05.039 --> 00:51:06.199
will tell you one thing...

00:51:07.400 --> 00:51:08.400
I love you.

00:51:30.639 --> 00:51:31.639
Boss,

00:51:31.719 --> 00:51:32.896
I'll go tell them to be quiet.

00:51:32.920 --> 00:51:33.920
No need.

00:51:37.800 --> 00:51:38.800
This is a good thing.